    <releaseNotes>
### Added
- Support ATLauncher share codes
- Allow changing metadata-server settings
- Add PolyMC icon as instance icon
- Add option to always hide Java setup wizard
- Add support for paste.gg, hastebin and mclo.gs paste services
- Add instance overrides for miscellaneous settings
- Modrinth modpack support
- Quilt mod metadata support
- Support Mojang's new split natives
- Allow changing CurseForge api key settings
- [macOS] Add Big Sur-style icon
- [Windows] Add Windows installer

### Changed
- Bump Qt requirement to 5.12
- Refactor launcher code
- Refactor network code
- Speedup automatic builds
- Make profile selection menu scrollable
- Switch to new CurseForge API Key
- Improve behavior when multiple mod loaders are in use
- Various improvements to ATLauncher support
- Switch to a better CurseForge icon
- Improve compile parameters

### Fixed
- Always build iconfix as static library
- Added and fixed mnemonics
- Fix selection of .zip files
- Fix graphical issue when moving toolbars
- Fix missing translations when switching languages
- Fix missing screenshots in screenshot manager
- Fix website link in CurseForge modpacks
- Hide temporary directory inside instances directory
- Fix icons not showing in some FTB modpacks
- Fix toolbar disappearing in a certain circumstance
- Fix issue with Solder.cf Technic packs
- [macOS] Fix Steam overlay on macOS

### Removed
- Remove unneeded build files
- Remove references to legacy Minecraft accounts
- Remove self-promotion from game client to reduce fingerprinting
- [macOS] Remove old macOS migration code

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/PolyMC/PolyMC/compare/1.2.2...1.3.0
</releaseNotes>
